profile:
The Colour and decor expert here to help with updating or personalizing your home!
I have worked in the paint industry for 10 years doing colour and decor consultations, matching and mixing colours, learning all the tricks on how to properly refinish any surface or room, while staying up to date with the latest colour trends. After I graduated from Fanshawe's Interior decorating program In 2013, I started having more requests for furnishing and fixture selecting as well as decor and colours.
In 2015 I decided to establish my own part-time decorating business to help with the full home-reno process, to provide advice in selecting furniture, finishes, decor, colours, as well as homestaging to help people sell their homes for higher dollar value. 
After many years in the paint industry, I decided to travel over to a large furniture store chain where I've increased their sales due to my visual merchandising, store decorating and space planning of all the products in the entire showroom. I also received many compliments from pre-existing customers noting how much better the store looks and how they can see a new decorator has taken over.
My passion is decorating and I can't wait to help you on your next project, no matter how big or small.
products: I can help order decor, the suppliers for flooring, tiling and cabinetry measure themselves for accuracy
services:
-Home Reno, Colour, Paint and/or Decor Consulations
-Interior Decorating
-Space Planning
-Home Staging
-Selecting of all furnishings
-Visual Merchandising
-Furniture, Cabinetry, and Flooring refinishing consultations
-Custom wall-art modifying 
-Exterior decorating
